    TrainMaster -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Bearer Token"| HF

    %% Ingress
    Route -->|"8265/TCP<br/>Edge TLS"| RayHead
    K8sIngress -->|"80/TCP HTTP<br/>Plaintext"| RayHead

